game.name: Horse Wedding Cake
game.description:
Horse Wedding Cake is a wonderful free online cooking game for girls from different age groups. You as a player will have to apply your culinary skills to prepare an extremely delicious horse wedding cake. Be careful while preparing the ingredients and following the recipe to ensure the optimum possible outcomes. Mix all the ingredients and create a proper dough that needs to be put in the microwave to be cooked. Once this job is done, also take care of its decoration part to make it look delicious. Do not forget to choose a color and a tasty design.

You are sure to have fun in unlimited amount when you explore all the tasks of this brand new cooking game for girls and boys. This super special wedding cake is basically inspired by Cinderella pumpkin carriage and much capable of leaving the positive impact on the mind of all wedding guests. Not only the guests, but it also impresses the grooms as well. Make sure that you follow the instructions with an open mind and try to make the mistakes as low as you can. 

Bet your craving for cake would increase after playing this game in your favourite browser! Check out all the details and do your best in order to create the best wedding cake you have ever made. Your good work will help to earn the appreciation from all the guests who attend the wedding. We know that you are not going to lose this opportunity. Good luck kids to have a blast in this best fun online cooking game!
